english:
{GHOST}
Welcooome.
You're in luck.
This very day, the {EIGHT SAGES}
open the path to the divine realm.

Ghost of {CALM}
Atop the central tower lies a magic
weapon, the {EARTH CRYSTAL}.
It breaks down living cells at the
molecular level.
\pGhost of {CALM}
With it you can destroy the {DEMON}
GOD's flesh. It now exists in this
world anchored to a dragon's body.

{WARRICK}
Yeah.
They took it, afraid the {DEMON GOD}
would turn it on them.

{RIDE}
Th-this is... the {PARASITE DEMON}
that killed {BARDAL}.
...This thing.

The {DEMON GOD}'s terrible power
affects all living things.
{FURNIS}, a sensitive {ELF},
most of all.\p{SETH}
Go on like this and she'll
waste away or go mad and die.
Worst case, the {DEMON GOD}
takes her body.\p{SETH}
We have the {SHIELD} to guard us...
but you two end here.

{RIDE}
...Right.
That old man knew I was a guardian
from the very start.
{RIDE}
Next thing I knew, he'd summoned the
hidden green dragon armor too.
He was waiting, fully prepared.
{RIDE}
Me getting here was his doing as
well.
More to the point, I don't see {REINA}
with {FURNIS}{...} did you send her home?

{STEINER}
Naive, {WARRICK}.
You'd have us fight as one now?
I have my own way.
I'll end the {DEMON GOD} my way.\p{STEINER}
Farewell, {WARRICK}.
